            was introduced in PR #15022 (`feat: Generate sourcemaps of friendly 
            call frames`), which added the `inputSourceMap` handling to the     
            generator's `SourceMap` class.\n\n### Fix\nThe minimal fix is to use
            optional chaining when accessing                                    
