            `undefined`, which is then passed to `setSourceContent`. The        
            `@jridgewell/gen-mapping` `setSourceContent` stores this as         
            `undefined` in its internal `_sourcesContent` array, and the        
            resulting source map's `sourcesContent` becomes `[undefined]`       
            â\x80\x94 which is the expected, non-crashing behavior (matching the
            snapshot in the test).\n\n### Verification\n- Reproduced the        
            original crash with a script, then confirmed it's fixed after the   
